{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_st02","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":20,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-ST-2","storyName":"启程","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"梦境已经结束，众人前进的道路却尚未终结。万众瞩目的时刻即将来临。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":18,"characters":["埃琳娜","多萝西","赫默","塞雷娅","赫默&塞雷娅","桑尼","格雷伊","玛丽","缪尔赛思","Mechanist","霍尔海雅","哥伦比亚雇佣兵","拓荒队成员","沉默的动力甲","克丽斯腾","？？？","莱茵研究员","星极"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"dialog","id":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5c/Avg_bg_29_g1_outdoorbase.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":5,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#6$1","id":7},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"多萝西......多萝西！你没事吧？！","id":8,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3e/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我很好。","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"慢、慢一点，你就快撞上我了......","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"都怪我，要是我早点发现斐尔迪南有问题，要是我能早点想办法提醒大家，要是我能多陪你聊一聊，要是......","id":13,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"你呀......从监控站一路赶过来，脸颊都沾上灰了。","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......也可能是揍斐尔迪南的时候沾上的。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我都忘了当时随手拿起来的是什么东西......我的手抖得很厉害。","id":19,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"你出气了吗？","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......不，我一点都不觉得爽快。","id":23,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"多萝西，我很失望，然后是愤怒，而当事情尘埃落定，我看着士兵们追着他冲出去......我又很难过。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"因为斐尔迪南做的这些事？","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bd/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"不，因为他......他本可以做到的事。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"要是我说，直到此刻，我都依然记得他教我的每一件事，依然相信诉说那些宏大的理想时，他眼里的光不完全是假的......","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"以及......我曾经最想要的......不过是他的认可......","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......我是不是特别傻？","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"这毫无问题，埃琳娜。","id":37,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"有时候......接受会比否定更难。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"你以后不再是任何人的助手。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"你身上不会有他的影子，可你的眼睛里留下了他燃过的火，你的起点正是他的终点，你无疑会走得比他更远。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"多萝西......","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你说这些话，怎么听起来像告别？什么叫我不再是任何人的助手......我知道你把自己接入“中枢”了，你的身体该不会出问题了吧？！","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/ce/Avg_avg_135_halo_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......别着急。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我真的没事，不信的话，你可以问问我们的好医生......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"character","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","fadetime":"1","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我什么都保证不了。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"奥利维亚，拓荒者们的身体检查都结束了？","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这里还有最后一位。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"唔......","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bd/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"“递质”仍在你们体内流动。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"目前你们的身体没有表现出任何异样，可未来的情况如何，谁都无法下判断。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"不必为我担心，亲爱的医生。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"这些流淌在我体内的物质，不会比生长在你们身上的结晶......和前方随时会降临的风暴更有威胁。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"可我们都不会因此停下，不是吗？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_4048_doroth_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......当然。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/65/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"character","id":76},{"type":"text","text":"失控的造物对基地的破坏很彻底。","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"眼前并没有多少废墟，只有满地银白留了下来。","id":78},{"type":"text","text":"要不了多久，就连它们都会被清理干净。","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"但是痕迹......痕迹终究存在。","id":80},{"type":"text","text":"面前的银色河流突然再次动了起来。","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"是雨云的倒影啊......","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_avg_108_silent_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":86},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":87},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":88},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_29_g7_mainstreet_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":89},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":90},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":92},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......消息已收到。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"基地的事情已由政府接手。按照约定，罗德岛需要将得到的情报销毁。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"但事情并不会就此结束。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#1$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"我刚得到了一条新的线索，关于斐尔迪南背后的支持者，我目前正在去见线人的路上。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"......","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_532_1#9$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞雷娅","text":"博士......","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_532_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"character","id":108},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9e/Avg_29_i09.png","xScale":"0.85","yScale":"0.85","fadetime":"0","id":109},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-40","xTo":"0","yFrom":"0","yTo":"0","duration":"40","xScaleFrom":"0.85","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleFrom":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.8","block":"false","id":110},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":112},{"type":"text","text":"塞雷娅停下了脚步，抬起头。","id":113},{"type":"text","text":"雨云正从城外的方向慢慢地飘过来。","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"一百多公里之外的基地里......","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"另一个人的脑子里也冒出了相同的念头。","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默&塞雷娅","text":"特里蒙就快下雨了。","id":117},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":120},{"type":"image","id":121},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5c/Avg_bg_29_g1_outdoorbase.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":122},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......到这里就可以了。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"谢谢你帮我们收拾东西，格雷伊。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"我很高兴自己能帮上一点忙，桑尼先生。","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_1027_greyy2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"而且能收拾的东西......呃，不太多。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_1027_greyy2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"挺好，和来的时候差不多。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"请务必向你的同事们传达我们的歉意与感谢。罗德岛的诸位的确就跟你说的一样，将我们从绝望的境地中拉了出来。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"不是的，桑尼先生，是您和其余拓荒者救了自己。","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_1027_greyy2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格雷伊","text":"您忘了吗？要不是您发出了“声音”，我们并没有机会抓住您的手。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/42/Avg_avg_1027_greyy2_1-9$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"拥有像你这样的朋友真是一桩幸事。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"工程师先生，我会记住你说的话，还有基地里发生的一切。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"还有玛丽......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"确保你们全部离开基地是我的工作。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#3$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我想说，你还有机会......逮捕我的机会。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"这次事件只是一场由个人违规行为引起的实验事故——这是上头给的说法。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"既然那几位莱茵的研究员也不准备再追究下去，你的“绑架”行为也不会被记录在案。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"不，我不是说这两天的事。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"是......四年前。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你知道我那一天晚上为什么想去报名参加实验吗？","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"每个拓荒者都有想回到城市里的理由。而我的理由是......","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我要回去找那个被我深深伤害过的人——我曾经最亲密的朋友。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我欠她一个道歉，以及——","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我的所作所为理应被审判。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我已经逃了四年多。最初我以为是荒野吞噬了我的梦想，让我变得越来越不像自己......","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"其实并不是。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"四年前的那一个夜晚，是我亲手杀死了过去那个追求公平正义的桑尼·罗马诺。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"要是被捕的话，你可能会面临两种惩罚。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"一种是进监狱，刑满之后进感染者收治区。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"另一种......","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"成为一名拓荒者，移动城市的入口永远对你封闭。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我知道。","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"那你已经是拓荒者了。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"这么说，你......","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#2$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"别再说什么原谅不原谅的话了，老朋友来送你一程，不该抓紧时间做点更有意义的事吗？","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":192},{"type":"character","id":193},{"type":"text","text":"一个久违的，温暖的拥抱。","id":194},{"type":"text","text":"是真正的重逢，也是时隔多年的正式告别。","id":195},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#3$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"想好之后去哪里了吗？","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"有个名字是D开头的一连串字母的人，前几天给我们发了一封有些古怪的邮件，附上了一则工作邀请。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我还没弄明白他是怎么拿到我们拓荒队的联系方式的......他一点都不像中介公司的人。","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#3$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"......下次接工作记得谨慎些。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_527_1#2$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛丽","text":"也别再尝试犯罪。否则的话，不管你跑多远，我都会把你揪回来。我保证。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_527_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"哈哈......","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b3/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#3$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"是，警长。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_535_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"character","id":211},{"type":"text","text":"拓荒队的兄弟姐妹们正在不远处呼喊他的名字。","id":212},{"type":"text","text":"桑尼知道，这一次，自己真正做好了启程的准备。","id":213},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":216},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_bg_29_g2_edgeofbase.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":217},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......基地的清理工作开始了。","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"-1","id":222},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"224","text":"明明是你们的能量科主任捅出来的篓子......"},"2":{"id":"224","text":"负责清理的依然是莱茵生命。"}},"values":[],"id":223},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":224,"end":226},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"嗯......这是莱茵身为大企业应当承担的社会责任吧？","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"-1","id":228},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"230","text":"我更愿意相信这是交易。"},"2":{"id":"230","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"230","text":"仅就这句话本身而言，我同意。"}},"values":[],"id":229},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":230,"end":234},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"好吧，会相信这说法的人都不在这里。","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"那些拓荒者......","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","focus":"-1","id":236},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"238","text":"你一直在看着他们，看了很久。"}},"values":[],"id":237},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":238,"end":252},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"他们又启程了。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"下一次......他们又会遇见什么呢？","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"一次又一次，循环往复......","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"以前的家已经回不去了，也许永远都不会有什么新的地方可以被称作家园。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"博士，我发现莱茵的人正在挖掘实验区的废墟......","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_521_1#1$1","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Mechanist","text":"......缪尔赛思主任，你也在这里。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_521_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"-1","id":254},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"256","text":"缪尔赛思......"}},"values":[],"id":255},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":256,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"259","text":"你想好什么时候回答我的问题了吗？"}},"values":[],"id":258},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":259,"end":265},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"问题......我在意的究竟是什么吗？","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"当我准备好开口的时候......","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你会知道的，Dr.{@nickname}。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":266},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":267},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":269},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_29_g7_mainstreet_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":273,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":274},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":275},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"......您放心，事情都处理好了，不会有民众知道359号基地发生了什么，更不可能有人拿这件事干扰您接下来的选举。","id":277,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"是的，我已经离开特里蒙，正在前往特区的路上。","id":279,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"斐尔迪南......","id":281,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"他不会再构成任何威胁了，我向您保证。","id":283,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":286},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_399_1#1$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"哥伦比亚雇佣兵","text":"女士......您、您明明就在莱茵生命外面，您为什么要欺骗副总统？","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_399_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"因为......","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#1$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我从来不会忘记自己最初的目标。","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":293},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":294},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":296},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":297},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":299,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mechawalk","volume":"0.5","id":300},{"type":"text","text":"他记不清楚自己走了多远。","id":301},{"type":"text","text":"喉咙里的刺痛与干涩提醒着他，他的身体经受不住这样的劳累。","id":302},{"type":"text","text":"可是......特里蒙仿佛就在身后。","id":303},{"type":"text","text":"又可能是在身前。","id":304},{"type":"text","text":"移动城市的阴影无比巨大，甚至随着时间的流逝而不断生长着。","id":305},{"type":"text","text":"他要尽快......尽快......","id":306},{"type":"text","text":"尽快去哪里？最近的接应地点......那里的人会不会和埃琳娜还有霍尔海雅一样，背叛他？","id":307},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","fadetime":"2","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"......站住。","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的动力甲","text":"......","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我们知道你是谁。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"斐尔迪南......你以为你在对我们做了那么多之后，还能安然无恙地一走了之吗？","id":317,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的动力甲","text":"......","id":319},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"别以为这铁东西能吓退我们。你只会夸夸其谈，并不能真正驾驭它。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"就算你对我们开火，把我们全部杀死在这里......","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"你也会遇到下一批拓荒者。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"看看你眼前的荒野吧，这里全都是你的敌人！","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_534_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的动力甲","text":"......","id":329},{"type":"text","text":"没有关系。","id":330},{"type":"text","text":"他亲手研发的“递质”就在手边，只要他选择注射，他就能瞬间让这动力甲听话，这些所谓的敌人全都不足为惧。","id":331},{"type":"text","text":"可是他为什么没有动？","id":332},{"type":"text","text":"是因为他不像多萝西，没有那个勇气吗？","id":333},{"type":"text","text":"还是因为......","id":334},{"type":"dialog","id":335},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":336},{"type":"text","text":"斐尔迪南，你才是那个被你眼中的宏大构想——被“时代”所抛下的人。","id":337},{"type":"text","text":"因为你从不认为自己正身处这个时代之中。","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"你口口声声说着把握当下，总是在思考，在操纵。你从不感受。","id":339},{"type":"text","text":"这是谁的声音？是......埃琳娜？","id":340},{"type":"text","text":"是啊，要是不想被抛下的话......他必须成为其中一部分。","id":341},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":343},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":344},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"character","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"沉默的动力甲","text":"......","id":347},{"type":"text","text":"动力甲沉默着，不再向前，也不再挣扎。","id":348},{"type":"text","text":"它举起了自己的双臂......","id":349},{"type":"text","text":"就像在拥抱面前的风、日光和大地一样。","id":350},{"type":"text","text":"愤怒的拓荒者们一拥而上，如同那头在基地上空咆哮的银色怪物——吞没了面前钢铁铸就的皮囊。","id":351},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":355},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_bg_29_g10_senioroffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":356},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":358,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"......梅兰德基金会对此事还有什么疑问？","id":360,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不，总辖女士。","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这一次我并非代表梅兰德而来。","id":363},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"......我的时间并不充裕。","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"正好，我也偏好有话直说。","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你回收了359号基地里实验中最核心的部分。","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"“中枢”被多萝西彻底摧毁——呈递给政府的报告上是这么写的。","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"而我恰巧看见了一支打扮低调的队伍，将某一辆封闭的载具开进了你的私人实验室。","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"塞雷娅说你放任了斐尔迪南......倒不如说，你利用了他。","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你最想要的东西，如今的确到了你的桌子上。","id":372},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"清扫359号基地是莱茵生命不得不承接的一项工作。","id":374,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"每天都会有无数失败实验的副产物被销毁。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"无论你以为自己看到的是什么，那都并不值得莱茵之外的任何人关注。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"销毁？当然，那破铜烂铁此刻肯定已经从你的桌上消失了。","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"证据可以被毁灭，记忆可以被篡改，但任何事件只要发生了，就一定会对后续事件产生影响。","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"洛肯，帕尔维斯，斐尔迪南......或许到了未来某个时间点，他们的名字不会留下任何记录。","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但历史的走向确实因他们而改变。","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可植入的施术单元，复活古代萨卡兹力量的嵌合技术，能被远程操控的动力甲，更大范围的精神实体网络......","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"下一项震撼这个时代的实验会是什么呢？","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"研究者只会探索一切可能性。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"我从不做预言。","id":389,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"假如记忆能够跨越时间的限制，预言不过就是重新发现被掩埋的历史。","id":391},{"type":"dialog","id":392},{"type":"character","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","fadetime":"1","id":394},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我们重新认识一下彼此吧，克丽斯腾·莱特。","id":396,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"我是霍尔海雅，历史学者，哥伦比亚占星研究协会名誉会长。","id":398,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#2$1","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"就让我冒昧地做一次预言——","id":400,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#2$1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霍尔海雅","text":"也许......很快我就会成为你最需要的合作伙伴。","id":402,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f9/Avg_avg_npc_536_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":405},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/49/Avg_bg_29_g9_headquarter.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":406},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_529_1#1$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵研究员","text":"星极小姐，埃琳娜研究员还没有回来。","id":409,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/93/Avg_avg_npc_529_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"嗯......她已经跟我说过。","id":411},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#7","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"我只是想在这里站一会，这样的话，等她一回来，我就能看见她。","id":413},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_529_1#1$1","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱茵研究员","text":"哈哈......有时候我真羡慕埃琳娜，能有这样关心着自己的姐姐。","id":415,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/93/Avg_avg_npc_529_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#7","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"唔......","id":417},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","id":419},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":420},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_536_1#3$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":421},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"150","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":422},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"character","fadetime":"2","id":425},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":426},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#7","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"那位女士是......","id":428},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#4","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"等等。","id":430},{"type":"character","name":"avg_274_Astesia_1#4","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星极","text":"天体仪......亮了？","id":432},{"type":"dialog","id":433},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":434},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":435},{"type":"character","id":436},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/00/Avg_29_i10.png","xScale":"0.85","yScale":"0.85","fadetime":"0","id":437},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-20","xTo":"0","yFrom":"-20","yTo":"0","duration":"40","xScaleFrom":"0.85","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleFrom":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.8","block":"false","id":438},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1","delay":"0.5","id":439,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":440},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":441},{"type":"text","text":"雨后的天幕总是格外清晰。","id":442},{"type":"text","text":"这是为数不多值得克丽斯腾走出实验室的理由之一。","id":443},{"type":"text","text":"她并非喜爱着那些闪耀着的光点。猜想如果无法被证实，就只是自欺欺人的谎言。","id":444},{"type":"text","text":"可谎言并不是毫无意义的。一个影子就算被扭曲了千万遍，也依然是某样真实之物的映射。","id":445},{"type":"text","text":"谎言之所以存在，只为了昭示一件事——真相也确实存在。","id":446},{"type":"text","text":"它就藏在这些闪耀的群星之间，而天幕并没有看起来那么遥远。","id":447},{"type":"text","text":"当她伸出手的时候，她一定能触碰到它——","id":448},{"type":"text","text":"触碰到那千万年来压在人们头顶的唯一真相。","id":449},{"type":"dialog","id":450},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":451},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":452},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":453},{"type":"character","id":454},{"type":"image","id":455}],"characters":["埃琳娜","多萝西","赫默","塞雷娅","赫默&塞雷娅","桑尼","格雷伊","玛丽","缪尔赛思","Mechanist","霍尔海雅","哥伦比亚雇佣兵","拓荒队成员","沉默的动力甲","克丽斯腾","？？？","莱茵研究员","星极"]}